{
  "data": [
    {
      "id": 18,
      "documentId": "mop1atojiqtaqfd5p6n4elj7",
      "title": "Food Safety Standards for Export-Ready Dried Vegetables",
      "slug": "food-safety-standards-for-export-ready-dried-vegetables",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Exporting dried vegetables to international markets requires strict adherence to food safety standards. For Kenyan producers, understanding and meeting these requirements is essential for accessing premium markets.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Key certifications for dried vegetable exports include:",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "- HACCP (Hazard Analysis Critical Control Point)— identifies and controls potential hazards throughout the production process",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "- ISO 22000— international standard for food safety management systems",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "- GlobalG.A.P. — good agricultural practices certification for farms",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "- Organic Certification — required for products marketed as organic in EU and US markets",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "AgroDakk Foods maintains rigorous quality control at every stage: from farm-level training on proper harvesting techniques to laboratory testing of finished products for contaminants, moisture content, and microbial safety.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Our processing facility follows strict hygiene protocols, and all products are traceable back to the specific farm and harvest date. This traceability is increasingly important for international buyers who want to verify the origin and quality of their food products.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "publishedDate": "2026-06-03",
      "excerpt": "Understanding the certifications, testing protocols, and quality measures required to export dried vegetables to European and Middle Eastern markets.",
      "author": "Mary Wanjiku",
      "featured": false,
      "createdAt": "2026-06-14T12:36:21.864Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-06-28T08:52:21.738Z",
      "publishedAt": "2026-06-28T08:52:21.804Z",
